      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based, <strong>hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish</strong> (don't have one? Start cooking in a large, wide-based pan then transfer to an oven-proof dish) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add <strong>half </strong>the<strong> sliced onion </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), <strong>crushed garlic</strong>, <strong>tomato wedges </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until the onion is beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-copy-3-1689773651336-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-copy-3-1689773651336-x400.jpg",
