            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the duck is cooking, add the <strong>remaining sliced onion</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar </strong>and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled red onion</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
