            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble your tacos, divide the <strong>duck carnitas</strong>, <strong>radish salsa</strong> and <strong>quick-pickled red onion </strong>evenly<strong> </strong>between the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> remaining chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
